---
import BaseHead from '../components/BaseHead.astro';
import Sidebar from '../components/Sidebar.astro';

---

<html lang="en">
	<head>
		<BaseHead title="The Zium Exposition" description="The Zium Exposition" />
		<style>

			body {
				font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
				margin: 0;
				padding: 0;
				display: flex;
				font-size: 14px;
				line-height: 1.6;
				color: #333;
				min-height: 100vh;

			}
			.content {
				flex-grow: 1;
				padding: 60px;
				max-width: 800px;
				width: 100%;
				box-sizing: border-box;
			}
			.game-section {
				margin-bottom: 60px;
			}
			.game-title {
				font-size: 24px;
				margin-bottom: 20px;
				font-family: 'Geist-Regular', sans-serif;


			}
			
			.image-gallery {
				display: flex;
				overflow-x: auto;
				gap: 20px;
				margin-bottom: 20px;
				padding-bottom: 10px;
				-webkit-overflow-scrolling: touch;
			}
			.gallery-item {
				flex: 0 0 auto;
				width: 100%;
				max-width: 533px;
				height: 300px;
			}
			.gallery-video {
				width: 100%;
				height: 100%;
			}
			.gallery-image {
				width: 100%;
				height: 100%;
				object-fit: cover;
			}
			.game-description {
				max-width: 600px;
				font-family: 'Geist-Regular', sans-serif;
				white-space: pre-wrap;

			}
			.game-credits {
				margin-top: 12px;
				max-width: 600px;
			}
			.game-credits ul {
				margin: 4px 0 0 0;
				padding-left: 20px;
			}
			.video-embed {
				position: relative;
				width: 100%;
				max-width: 600px;
				padding-top: 56.25%; /* 16:9 aspect ratio */
				margin: 20px 0;
			}
			.video-embed iframe {
				position: absolute;
				top: 0;
				left: 0;
				width: 100%;
				height: 100%;
				border: 0;
			}
			@media (max-width: 768px) {
				body {
					flex-direction: column;
				}
				.content {
					padding: 20px;
				}
				.game-title {
					font-size: 20px;
				}
				.gallery-item {
					height: 56.25vw; /* 16:9 aspect ratio */
					max-height: 300px;
				}
				.game-description {
					font-size: 14px;
				}
			}
		</style>
	</head>
	<body>
		<Sidebar />
		<div class="content">
			<strong>Movements and Modulations in The Zium Exposition</strong>
			<br>
			<br>
			Playtime: 7-10 minutes (loops indefinitely)
			<br>
			Platform: Windows, Mac

			<p>
			The Zium Exposition is a Museum Exploration Game filled with artwork and installations from artists around the world, working in various mediums and styles.
			<br>

            <p>
			For my piece, I created an intimate virtual space that contains a dancer. The player can view the dancer from different angles as light and shadows stretch around the room. If players enter the space after 10pm, the musical score changes to a more franctic and chaotic version. The lights and wall prefabs rapidly change, creating a more strobe light experience. 
            
            <p>Original music was composed by <a href="https://languageinstinct.bandcamp.com/" target="_blank">Gregory Nunn</a>.</p>
			<br>

			<div class="video-embed">
                <iframe 
                    width="560" 
                    height="315" 
                    src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/6PZblTnbxgg?si=jPtwOeG644bQi5wW" 
                    title="YouTube video player" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" referrerpolicy="strict-origin-when-cross-origin" allowfullscreen></iframe>
			</div>
			<br>
            <img  src="/zium-exposition-poster.png"/>
			<br>

			<!-- <div style="width: 25%;">
			<img src="/Written-By-a-Human-Not-By-AI-Badge-white@2x.png" alt="Your Image">
			</div> -->

		</div>
	</body>
</html>